{
  "stem": "2723.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My sister developed a fantasy world, centering around Palestine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She dreamed of Palestine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And knowing that my father was there, this got fed on the little bits that we knew about Palestine from probably underground infiltration of various-- what are they called, the people who come?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I've lost the names, suddenly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], who came across.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she built that up into colossal extent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe it was my probably lesser strong character that went the opposite way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, at that stage, felt why am I to make such a thing of being Jewish when I am being hounded for it?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I just probably, really instinctively, went the other way, so much so that I very much remember that I resented strongly that I couldn't do this, that, and the other, and would have loved to cheat and get into movies under false pretenses, which would have necessitated pretending to be non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My sister would have never done that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My sister was very sporty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was very clumsy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we had very real differences.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Probably we would have gone into fire for each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that was probably never tested, or put to the test.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had a fair few fights.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She was very, very pretty in a very strongly Jewish way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was always bemoaning the fact that I had sparse hair.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She has-- she had a wonderful head of hair.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And one of the joys I do recall-- the closeness was when I could brush it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She hated it, but I loved doing it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do, thanks to my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I found some drawings that she had done the year-- probably very close to the end of her life, which reflects an imagined group of Jewish children in a kind of [NON-ENGLISH], a conference.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
